text: Hi Nathalie, I am still here

Oh hey, good to hear from you. Was starting to worry since you didn't reply. Hope everything is going alright? I finished my dissertation so I am back doing my practical stuff. How is the showreel coming along?
I am currently working on my final project which is due in may. It is supposed to contain glass bottles. As it turns out that is a lot harder to set up than I expected. Do you have any tips on that?
